英国当地时间2014年7月23日23:40，'''[[第20届英联邦运动会|第20届英联邦运动会]]开幕典礼'''在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]][[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]][[凯尔特人公园球场|凯尔特人公园球场]]举行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2014/jul/24/commonwealth-games-opening-ceremony-glasgow-review|title=Commonwealth Games opening ceremony review – no lack of heart but a lack of oomph|last=Gardner|first=Lyn|authorlink=Lyn Gardner|date=2014-07-24|website=[[卫报|卫报]]|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2014-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724080953/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2014/jul/24/commonwealth-games-opening-ceremony-glasgow-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。71名运动员手持国家和地区旗帜，带领所属国家代表团游行到体育场。英女王[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]宣布运动会正式开幕，并称英联邦有“共同理想和抱负”和团结各成员的纽带<ref>{{cite news|last=Duncanson|first=Hilary|date=23 July 2014|title=Queen tells of 'shared ideals' at Commonwealth Games opening ceremony|url=http://www.independent.ie/world-news/europe/queen-tells-of-shared-ideals-at-commonwealth-games-opening-ceremony-30455671.html|newspaper=Irish Independent|publisher=Independent News & Media|agency=[[美联社|美联社]]|accessdate=2014-07-24|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523042728/http://www.independent.ie/world-news/europe/queen-tells-of-shared-ideals-at-commonwealth-games-opening-ceremony-30455671.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

演出动用约2000名演员，包括[[卡伦·邓巴|卡伦·邓巴]]、[[约翰·罗巴曼|约翰·罗巴曼]]、[[罗德·斯图尔特|罗德·斯图尔特]]、[[苏珊·波伊尔|苏珊·波伊尔]]、[[巴古拉·贝内德蒂|巴古拉·贝内德蒂]]、[[朱莉·弗丽丝|朱莉·弗丽丝]]，还有来自[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]的贺电。倒计时拉开了典礼的大幕，随后苏格兰演员[[伊万·麦克格雷格|伊万·麦克格雷格]]的视频诠释了赛事与[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]的合作伙伴关系<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/commonwealth-games/commonwealth-games-2014-opening-ceremony-ewan-mcgregor-launches-unicef-charity-fundraiser-during-performance-9624536.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-27 |archive-date=2014-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727002715/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/commonwealth-games/commonwealth-games-2014-opening-ceremony-ewan-mcgregor-launches-unicef-charity-fundraiser-during-performance-9624536.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。基金会为了拯救和改变孩子们的生活，而与赛会达成独特的合作伙伴关系，旨在“利用体育给予每一位苏格兰儿童的力量，造福所有英联邦国家和地区的儿童<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.glasgow2014.com/about-us/our-sponsors/unicef |title=Unicef | Glasgow 2014 - Commonwealth Games |publisher=Glasgow 2014 |date= |accessdate=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2014-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729134817/http://www.glasgow2014.com/about-us/our-sponsors/unicef |dead-url=no }}</ref>”。

[[英国广播公司第一台|BBC一台]]全程转播开幕礼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04bb2b1 |title=BBC One - Commonwealth Games, Glasgow 2014, Opening Ceremony |publisher=bbc.co.uk |date=2014-07-23 |accessdate=2014-07-23 |archive-date=2014-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723173804/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04bb2b1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2703216/Tunnocks-Tea-Cakes-Irn-Bru-Forth-Bridge-Gretna-Green-Glasgow-opens-Commonwealth-Games-world-Scottish-flavour.html|title= A giant haggis, cabers, golf clubs, 41 Scottish terriers, Rod Stewart, Billy Connolly, the Queen, lashings of self-deprecation and even a gay kiss - Glasgow's Commonwealth Games begin in style|date= 2014-07-24|work= Daily Mail|accessdate= 2014-07-24|archive-date= 2014-07-24|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140724030647/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2703216/Tunnocks-Tea-Cakes-Irn-Bru-Forth-Bridge-Gretna-Green-Glasgow-opens-Commonwealth-Games-world-Scottish-flavour.html|dead-url= no}}</ref> ，全世界预计有10亿电视观众<ref name=telegraph>{{cite web |author=Commonwealth Games |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/commonwealthgames/10987581/Commonwealth-Games-2014-the-Queen-laughs-off-baton-hitch.html |title=Commonwealth Games 2014: the Queen laughs off baton hitch |publisher=Telegraph |date= |accessdate=14 July 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727075340/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/commonwealthgames/10987581/Commonwealth-Games-2014-the-Queen-laughs-off-baton-hitch.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，有900万英国观众收看典礼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a586161/commonwealth-games-2014-opening-ceremony-scores-76m-on-bbc-one.html |title=Commonwealth Games 2014 opening ceremony scores 7.6m on BBC One - TV News |publisher=Digital Spy |date= |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2014-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140727184625/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a586161/commonwealth-games-2014-opening-ceremony-scores-76m-on-bbc-one.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

